Version 1.1 Roadmap

App
* Add in all favorites (currently limited to 100)
* Add in animation on treasuries and explore using arrows
* Explore using arrows for homepage
* Add in-app cart functionality
* Add the ability to see a user's shop
* Add Treasuries and Users to favorites
* Fill out the product detail with user information
* Fill out the treasuries with "X hours ago"
* Add advertisements and release a free version.
* Add more analytics
* Add Twitter
* Add Pinterest
* Add settings page (Where we would have the signout buttons, instructions, etc.
* Add load timestamp to the homepage.
* Upgrade to Cordova 1.6.1
* Add messaging and validation to the search panel

Backend
* Use Express and MongoDB to cache results from Etsy

